    <p>At the heart of all we do is the teaching of the Bible as God's key instrument for announcing that Jesus Christ is the rightful Ruler of the world and of each one of us. (See <a href="">'What we believe'</a> for further details).</p>
	<p>We encourage people to become active followers of Jesus Christ, and provide opportunities for them to grow in their faith and love. We welcome people of all ages and backgrounds to find out the good news of Jesus Christ who, by his death on the cross, can rescue us from God's rightful displeasure.</p>

